author: Doug Sharpe
description:
There has been a long standing internet theory that Donald Duck suffers from PTSD, though Disney has never official acknowledged it, many soldiers returning from WW2 strongly identified with Donald and his experience during the war, so it seems like comic book artists continued story lines that reflected the struggles Donald would have had coming home and readjusting to peace in the same way his military films reflected the struggles soldiers were having on the front lines. 

And to all the men, women and their families at home, past and present, who have fought to guarantee me the freedoms I get to enjoy everyday. 

*Thank you for your service, I don’t forget*
title: Does Donald Duck Suffer From PTSD?
